BEGIN_PGML

You have set up the following block system such that blocks [`\textrm{A}`] and [`\textrm{B}`] are connected by a rope with tension [`\textrm{T}`]. 
You want to cause block [`\textrm{B}`] to either tip or slip along the ground without touching it. So instead you decide to apply a force [`\textrm{P}`]
on block [`\textrm{B}`].

