a width [`w = [$w]\ m`]. The rope connects at a height [`h_1 = [$h1]\ m`] and the coefficients of static and kinetic friction are given as [`\mu_s = [$mus]`]
and [`\mu_k = [$muk]`]. Find the force [`\textrm{P}`] required to move the blocks and the tension [`\textrm{T}`] present in the ropes at that moment.

